    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that there are different theories, but you can't really compare them as equals if one is based on the actual text and the other is just based on how people feel about society changing, right? like, isn't originalism fundamentally more \"accurate\" because it's tied to the historical reality of when the law was written?",
